{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'W-welcome back... M-mast—', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Are we roleplaying?', 3: '6', 4: 'What are you doing?', 5: '8'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'No. This is training.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'This is... an additional exercise for the training...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Apart from combat and tactics... I thought of a way to assist you in your daily life, Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "So I thought I'd give it a try.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'I can wake you up every morning and prepare breakfast for you.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'I can prepare tea, coffee, or cute little cakes for you during your free time.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'I can even prepare your bed for you before you go to bed at night.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Like a fam... or a maid.', 4: '1'}
{2: "Isn't that too luxurious for the lives we have right now?", 3: '17', 4: "I don't think Constructs are needed for these kinds of work.", 5: '18'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "I'm preparing for the inevitable future...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "It's something I want to do.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'I believe that with you and everyone, we will reclaim Earth one day...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "And when we find each other on the surface, we would still be the commandant's Gray Ravens, right?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Of course.', 3: '22', 4: "As long as our squad isn't disbanded.", 5: '22'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Then this training is necessary.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Like, the way we greet each other when me meet...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'W-welcome back... M-mast—', 4: '1'}
{2: 'This is too embarrassing!', 3: '27', 4: 'You really don\'t have to call me "master."', 5: '28'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "I'm actually quite embarrassed as well... How about I call you something else?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Is that so? I thought you would enjoy being called that... In that case—', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Welcome back, Commandant.', 4: '1'}
